As far as the camera specifications are concerned, Tecno Pop 5C features a dual-camera at the rear which includes a 5-megapixel rear camera and a 2-megapixel selfie camera. The camera app has various modes including AI Face Beauty, HDR, Smile Shit, AI Sticker, and Bokeh mode. The smartphone houses a 2,400mAh battery. For connectivity, the Tecno Pop 5C comes with support Bluetooth v4.2, Wi-Fi 2.4GHz, GPS, GSM, Nano-SIM, Micro-USB port, GPRS, FM, and more. There are sensors including G-sensor and proximity sensor.
